# LLM Provider Configuration
# ===========================
# Supported providers: openai, anthropic
#
# Provider Selection:
# 1. If LLM_PROVIDER is set, that provider will be used
# 2. If not set, auto-detects from available API keys
# 3. When both keys are present, defaults to anthropic
#
# Uncomment to explicitly set provider:
# LLM_PROVIDER=openai
# LLM_PROVIDER=anthropic

# API Keys
# ========
# Set at least one API key below

# OpenAI API Key
# Required for: OpenAI LLM models, embeddings
# Get your key at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-...

# Anthropic API Key
# Required for: Claude LLM models
# Get your key at: https://console.anthropic.com/
# Note: Embeddings still use OpenAI even when using Claude
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Model Information
# =================
# Default models used when provider is auto-detected:
#
# OpenAI:
#   - LLM: gpt-4o-mini
#   - Embeddings: text-embedding-3-large
#
# Anthropic:
#   - LLM: claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022
#   - Embeddings: text-embedding-3-large (OpenAI)
